{"tid":2515947,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜琪峯鼓勵年輕人不要受目前問題所困 要放眼將來","createTime":"2021-05-04T10:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T10:21:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0aac398c89617c416228a3fb375dbcf70c8b023","tid":2515947,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"杜琪峯（杜sir）、鄭欣宜（Joyce）及MIRROR成員盧瀚霆（Anson Lo），今日到尖沙嘴出席虛擬銀行卡發佈會。做導演超過40年的杜sir，今次處男演出拍廣告，杜sir自認是演戲新人，他笑言︰「入行40幾年嚟，未試過喺片場咁舒服，導演叫我做乜就做乜，覺得係好體驗，做演員真係好舒服，冇負擔享受拍片，如果有人請會繼續做。」杜sir表示會與ViuTV合作拍劇集，他鼓勵年輕人不要受目前問題所困，要放眼將來，他說︰「年輕人係為將來而活。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210504/FSOYCZUHBFDJPIEQBFRHKDQRZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210504%2FFSOYCZUHBFDJPIEQBFRHKDQRZE%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnlBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=83a1b3ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210504%2FFSOYCZUHBFDJPIEQBFRHKDQRZE%2F&h=176fdf92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210504/FSOYCZUHBFDJPIEQBFRHKDQRZE/</a>"},{"pid":"e32f1bc086bd32d2bf62c14c332a5dc47b5f1053","tid":2515947,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"杜sir繼續戴FDMNOL口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}